  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of a short-term emotional stimulation on
      the mood of healthy persons.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The trial assesses the effects of a emotion-centered stimulation on the mood of healthy
      persons. The outcomes will be evaluated with standard questionnaires.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
